hey guys made this a while ago but a friend send i should upload it duo to have must fun it is.

this is a sonic based map and is allso based off sven coop map breakfree that gave me the idea.

the floor keeps going up while you work your way round traps.
there is 2  boss fights. the 1st one you just need to stay alive for 60 seconds the other you get the fight.

its alot of fun  with epic music and players love it.  sonic helps you out plus dr eggman is in it.

im  working on a  follow up to this but it being a sonic course map on the dr eggman ship.  its about 20 % done and looking nice
